Maintain close contact and communication with other institutional investors, listed companies, and researchers in the market;

5）完成部门和公司交办的其他事项。

Organize the implementation and completion of other matters assigned by the department and the company.

Our client, a well-established investment firm to invite high caliber candidates to join their company.

